---
title: Smoked Ham & Cheese Sub Salad with Tomato, Onion & Creamy Italian Dressing
description: A deli-style ham and cheese sub in salad form? Don’t mind if we do! You’ll toss crisp lettuce with smoky diced ham, a blend of Italian cheeses, and oregano-seasoned tomato and onion in creamy, tangy Italian dressing. And boom—you’re ready for lunch in a lightning-fast 15 minutes (no waiting in line!).
